        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nHi Mandeep,\n\ncurrently CLI uses 30261 and i believe sdnc will have something different. How it is conflicting with sdnc ? As CLI already uses this port i would like to understand before committing the changes.\n\nThanks.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
